summary: Player Home with a Tower from the West of The Reach!
descriptionHtml:
Helllo Everyone!

Here is my 5th MOD, I've not modded in awhile! ^_^

Requirements:
Skyrim.esm

Description:

A Player Home Farm that is very basic with a Tower and Well. It sits high on a rocky slope by the ever-flowing river! With lovely views!
It is 2 stories, with lots of space inside to hold things in chests. No manequins or Weapon racks, sorry!

Outside there are; a forege, alchemy table and an enchanting table!Â 

Although, since it is in the middle of no-where, there is Saber Cats, wolfs and bandits around it! You may have to fight them off!

Bugs: None so far, only thing is its quite basic! :P
